.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, scientific, epic, thriller
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, game, old-henry, bluemaster
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the game-smoker is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
6. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere between the vegafina-smoker and the game-smoker##7
7. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre      | scientific | martial-arts      | epic | thriller     |
| Cigar   | vegafina    | bluemaster | game   | old-henry |

