.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, hot-chocolate
House: gothic-revival, victorian, colonial, art-deco
1. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the victorian house##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
4. the art-deco house is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person drinking mirinda##7
5. the colonial house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
6. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the colonial house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage          | hot-chocolate    | cola   | fanta | mirinda  |
| House   | gothic-revival | colonial | art-deco    | victorian |

