.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, azure, fuchsia, ebony
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, documentary, western, epic
1. the person who likes azure is not the person watching epic movies##6
2. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
3. the person who likes ebony is the person watching western movies##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere between the person who likes ebony and the person who likes yellow##7
5. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Color   | ebony | fuchsia | azure | yellow |
| Movie-Genre           | western   | epic    | horror       | documentary  |

