.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, rat, bird, ferret
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, white, orange, aquamarine
1. the owner of the mouse is not the person who likes lilac##6
2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
4. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
5. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the person who likes aquamarine and the owner of the rat##7
6. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person who likes orange##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Pet           | ferret | mouse | bird | rat |
| Color   | aquamarine         | orange      | lilac | white            |

