.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
4 different games are played: bridge, whist, backgammon, canasta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, rowing, biathlon, ice-hockey
1. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##7
2. the person playing whist is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6
3. the person who's sport is rowing is not the person playing backgammon##6
4. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
5. the person playing bridge is the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Game   | bridge | canasta | whist | backgammon |
| Sport           | soccer    | rowing   | ice-hockey  | biathlon      |

