.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, boat, ship, jet-ski
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, nectarine, cranberry, plum
1. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person eating eggplant##5
2. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
3. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the boat and the person eating nectarine##2
6. the person eating cranberry is somewhere between the person eating nectarine and the person driving the boat##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Transport   | jet-ski | roller | boat | ship   |
| Food   | nectarine    | cranberry      | eggplant      | plum |

