2. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating pear##1
3. the mechanic is not the person eating pear##6
4. the person eating cherry is on the left of the paramedic##1
5. the accountant is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
6. the person eating plum is somewhere between the person eating pear and the person eating cherry##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Food   | cherry | plum | potato | pear |
| Job   | mechanic  | paramedic    | videographer    | accountant  |

