2. the fan classical is the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is the fan trance##1
4. the fan trance is not the person who growsmarigold##6
5. the fan trance is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere between the person who growsorchid and the fan trance##7
7. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
