4. the person who likes black is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person who likes amber##5
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who likes black##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Transport      | airplane   | helicopter | motorbike | trike   |
