4. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere between the person who likes amber and the person playing mah-jongg##7
5. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the person who likes mauve##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
