2. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
3. the person who likes apricot is not the person playing canasta##6
4. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
5. the person playing snooker is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the person who likes apricot##7
6. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
7. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Color           | apricot | purple  | turquise  | mauve |
| Game   | backgammon  | snooker | canasta | bridge   |

