1. the thai is somewhere between the engineer and the italian##7
2. the engineer is on the right of the mechanic##1
3. the australian is on the left of the argentine##1
4. the mechanic is somewhere to the right of the thai##5
5. the thai is on the left or right of the coach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Nationality         | italian    | thai | australian     | argentine |
| Job   | coach | writer  | mechanic | engineer |

 